entry.title: 0.8.6 release candidate 1
entry.summary: It has been brought to attention that the bitcoin.org website is in need of an update as it still points downloads to version 0.8.5. It is unclear who is responsible for maintaining and updating the website, but it is necessary to ensure that users are able to access the latest version of the software. The HTML attachment included with this context may contain further information or instructions regarding this issue.
